<p><em>Everything you need to understand before the core concept makes sense — explained from scratch.</em></p>
{{FOUNDATIONS}}

<hr>

<h2>The Concept: {{CONCEPT_TITLE}}</h2>
{{CONCEPT_EXPLANATION}}

